message.entry: Specified crop window format is not supported. The crop window must be either a 1x6 vector of the form [x,y,z,w,h,d] or an images.spatialref.Cuboid object.
The crop window does not intersect the volume.
The crop window is out of bounds of the input volume. \nThe lower bound should be >= 1 and the upper bound should not exceed the image size.
